full_text: Case 1:20-cr-00330-PAE Document 747 Filed 08/10/22 Page 166 of 228 842 LC2Qmax5 - corrected Alessi - Direct spa. Q. What did this girl look like? A. She look -- she look young. She have blond hair, and she had a long white uniform, like a nurse's uniform. Q. What did you see Ms. Maxwell do after she got out of the car? A. They talk briefly, and they went back to the spa. Q. Who talked? A. Ms. Maxwell and Ms. Roberts. Q. Is that the girl? A. Yes. Q. And then where did you see Ms. Maxwell and the girl go? A. They went inside the spa. And couple minutes later Ms. Maxwell came out, got in the car, and we left. Q. When was the next time you saw that girl from the Mar-a-Lago parking lot? A. The next time I saw her was late that afternoon, around 5:00, 6:00 in the afternoon. Q. Where did you see her? A. At the house in Palm Beach. Q. And when she arrived, where did she go? A. She went -- I introduce her to Ms. Maxwell at her desk. Q. Did you learn her name? A. No. Q. At some point did you learn her name? SOUTHERN DISTRICT REPORTERS, P.C. (212) 805-0300 DOJ-OGR-00012451
